# Plan — Client Finder 1.0
slug: `client-finder-1-0` | richness: 10/10 | full production-quality | STATUS: READY

---

## Demo Concept (confirmed)

**Hero:** Interactive Lead CRM table — sortable, filterable, searchable; inline status editing; bulk ops; CSV export; KPI summary bar.
**Supporting 1:** "Run Discovery" panel — industry/region pickers, animated multi-step pipeline (Search → Scrape → WebGPU Audit → Enrich), appends realistic new leads.
**Supporting 2:** WebGPU Audit module — real `navigator.gpu` capability check + hardware adapter info; loads `HuggingFaceTB/SmolVLM-256M-Instruct` via `@huggingface/transformers` v3 WebGPU backend for live in-browser vision inference; WASM fallback if WebGPU unavailable.
**Drill-down modal:** per-lead detail — homepage screenshot, audit sub-scores (Modernity/Mobile/Function 1-10 each), AI rationale text, outdated-stack flags, decision-maker card (name, title, seniority, LinkedIn-style stub).

Stub (rule-1): external APIs (Serper, Apollo, live scraping) — real pipeline architecture shown but data is seeded/mock. Rationale: keys/cost/ToS/bot-ban risk. Note: Proxycurl is defunct (shut down Jan 2025) — Apollo.io is the enrichment API throughout.

