## Design Tokens (finalized)

### Palette
```
--cf-bg:           #060B18   /* near-black navy */
--cf-surface:      #0D1526   /* card/panel surface */
--cf-surface-2:    #142034   /* elevated surface, modal bg */
--cf-border:       #1E3050   /* subtle borders */
--cf-primary:      #4F6EF7   /* electric blue — CTAs, links, active states */
--cf-primary-h:    #3B58E5   /* primary hover */
--cf-accent:       #7C3AED   /* violet — secondary highlights */
--cf-text:         #E8EDF5   /* primary text */
--cf-subtext:      #7A8BA8   /* secondary/meta text */
--cf-muted:        #3D5070   /* disabled, placeholder */

/* Score chips */
--cf-score-high:   #10B981   /* green — 7-10 */
--cf-score-mid:    #F59E0B   /* amber — 4-6 */
--cf-score-low:    #EF4444   /* red — 1-3 */

/* Outreach status badges */
--cf-status-new:         #60A5FA  /* blue */
--cf-status-contacted:   #34D399  /* green */
--cf-status-inprogress:  #FBBF24  /* amber */
--cf-status-ignored:     #6B7280  /* gray */
```

### Typography
- **UI/body:** `Inter` (Google Fonts) — weights 300/400/500/600/700
- **Tabular data/scores:** `Inter` + `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-feature-settings: "tnum"`
- **Monospace (stack flags, code snippets):** `JetBrains Mono` — small text only
- Base size: 14px, line-height 1.5; table cells 13px; heading scale 18/22/28px

