## Feasibility Assessment (post-research)

| Area | Verdict | Notes |
|------|---------|-------|
| CRM table + filters | Feasible | Standard React pattern |
| Drill-down modal | Feasible | Two-panel layout |
| Discovery pipeline animation | Feasible | CSS + setTimeout |
| WebGPU detection | Feasible | 3-line navigator.gpu check |
| WebGPU real inference (SmolVLM-256M) | Feasible | Confirmed by researcher; 15-25s first load, WASM fallback |
| Apollo DM card (masked names) | Feasible | Graceful partial-name display |
| Flask blueprint | Feasible | Mirror spotify_blueprint.py pattern |
| Seed data 50 leads | Feasible | Static JS seedLeads.js + blueprint init |
| Vite build | Feasible | ~2-3 min |
| Total files | 14 | Slightly over 12-file soft cap; justified richness 10 |

**Status: READY.** All research questions answered. No remaining blockers. WebGPU real inference confirmed feasible (SmolVLM-256M-Instruct). Proxycurl replaced with Apollo throughout. Demo-builder can proceed.

